Package gobblin.data.management.copy.predicates

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    AlwaysTrue<T>
    Predicate that is always true.
    NonPartitionTableRegistrationTimeSkipPredicate
    A fast table skip predicate that reads the parameter HiveDataset.REGISTRATION_GENERATION_TIME_MILLIS from the Hive non partition table and skips the copy if it is newer than the modification time of the location of the source table.
    RegistrationTimeSkipPredicate
    A fast partition skip predicate that reads the parameter HiveDataset.REGISTRATION_GENERATION_TIME_MILLIS from the Hive partition and skips the copy if it is newer than the modification time of the location of the source partition.
    RootDirectoryModtimeSkipPredicate
    Use with HiveCopyEntityHelper.FAST_PARTITION_SKIP_PREDICATE.
